title: Riot Girl Tristana EUW link not working

embed.description: "Wanna see the fireworks?" - Riot Girl Tristana

body: Hello, I can't get the skin, it just says "Sorry, Riot Girl Tristana will be back shortly.", but the other regions seem to work, so if someone can help me.

replies.body: The promos are pretty old and can get buggy sometimes.  :(  She should be on your account now!
Thank you for your help! I was wondering why I had her unlocked even tho I didn't log out and didn't receive "a gift from riot" notification.
http://woobox.com/pmrvz4 I can't get the skin too ;( ''It says Sorry, Riot Girl Tristana will be back shortly''
Make post like me on Help & Support, it got solved quickly after that.
